.TH "LIGHTNING-PEER-LIST" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-peer-list \- list connected Lightning network peers
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning peer-list
.SH DESCRIPTION
Lists all known peers from the CLN daemon via
.BR lightning-cli (1)
.BR listpeers .
Returns a JSON array of objects:
.nf
[{"peer_id":"...","connected":true,"num_channels":N}, ...]
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Success (empty array if no peers or daemon unavailable).
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-peer (1),
.BR lightning-peer-connect (1),
.BR lightning-peer-disconnect (1)
